  %h1.center It Does Nothing, but it does it Really Well.
%pre{ :style => 'width: 800px; margin: auto;' }
  rails new application_name --skip-test-unit --skip-prototype \
  &nbsp;&nbsp;--template=https://github.com/sampierson/rails-templates/raw/master/itdoesnothing.rb
  cd application_name
