  heroku config:add BUNDLE_WITHOUT="development:test"
  git push heroku master
  heroku rake db:migrate
  heroku addons:add sendgrid:free
%h2 What is it?
%p
  ItDoesNothing is a Rails application template that creates a functional website that is not yet purposed for a
  specific application.
  This website was entirely created then deployed to Heruoku using just the above commands.
  ItDoesNothing includes:
